graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|core platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.22+]
    Kueue -->|metrics protection| RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|optional cert mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Kueue -.->|optional metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Integration Points)
    Kueue -->|queue ML jobs| TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>Kubeflow]
    Kueue -->|queue Ray workloads| RayOp[Ray Operator]
    Kueue -->|queue batch jobs| BatchJobs[Kubernetes Jobs<br/>batch/v1]
    Kueue -->|queue jobsets| JobSetOp[JobSet Operator]

    %% External Services
    Kueue -->|node provisioning| ClusterAutoscaler[Cluster Autoscaler]
    Kueue -.->|multi-cluster| RemoteClusters[Remote K8s Clusters]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    PrometheusOp -->|scrapes metrics| Kueue

    %% Workload Frameworks Supported
    subgraph "Supported Workload Frameworks"
        TrainingOp -->|manages| PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob]
        TrainingOp -->|manages| TFJob[TFJob]
        TrainingOp -->|manages| MPIJob[MPIJob]
        TrainingOp -->|manages| MXJob[MXJob]
        TrainingOp -->|manages| XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob]
        TrainingOp -->|manages| PaddleJob[PaddleJob]

        RayOp -->|manages| RayJob[RayJob]
        RayOp -->|manages| RayCluster[RayCluster]

        JobSetOp -->|manages| JobSet[JobSet]
    end

    %% Integration Details
    K8s -->|provides API| Kueue
    K8s -->|calls webhooks| Kueue
    K8s -->|aggregates API| Kueue

    %% CRDs Watched/Created
    subgraph "Kueue CRDs"
        ClusterQueue[ClusterQueue<br/>v1beta1]
        LocalQueue[LocalQueue<br/>v1beta1]
        Workload[Workload<br/>v1beta1]
        AdmissionCheck[AdmissionCheck<br/>v1beta1]
        ResourceFlavor[ResourceFlavor<br/>v1beta1]
        WorkloadPriorityClass[WorkloadPriorityClass<br/>v1beta1]
        MultiKueueCluster[MultiKueueCluster<br/>v1alpha1]
        MultiKueueConfig[MultiKueueConfig<br/>v1alpha1]
    end

    Kueue -->|manages| ClusterQueue
